{"tid":693810,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實恥笑00後嘅人有幾多係思想成熟丫","createTime":"2018-06-07T19:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T13:16:45.000Z","uid":100347,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67faae553fdbc79d8942cfcdcd72ad9c1d882e64","tid":693810,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"話00後多垃圾，愛國染紅。<br />\n<br />\n其實90後垃圾唔多咩？普教中較少、洗腦教育又少<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢話好少，但一定少過00後洗腦教育。<br />\n<br />\n00後讀普教中嘅比率一定多過90後喎<br />\n<br />\n當年班8、90愛中國情懷仲勁過而家班00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話捐錢去四川熊貓個學生、08北京奧運，諗到啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地應該做嘅 係希望00後融入返 去改變佢地而唔係用一個標籤去list人囉<br />\n<br />\n點解唔笑得？ 笑 係可以笑，但我見啲戇鳩仔開口埋口標籤人00後真心覺得好弱智。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知呢啲係五毛定真係戇鳩仔 但永遠唔會見佢地拎00後嘅精英同自己比"},{"pid":"8d1e6311332b6c232e57aa45bdc9976806d6080c","tid":693810,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T19:45:12.000Z","msg":"好多人俾人煽動左去反00後<br />\n<br />\n其實00後係我地呢代最需要去「拉攏」既一代"},{"pid":"46ca9dd865078a389ce4604a026b13928a72815a","tid":693810,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T19:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/034555_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F034555_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e87b1792&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"854a8b603a394e478176d4a03a57f1cf455c4b63","tid":693810,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d1e6311332b6c232e57aa45bdc9976806d6080c","tid":693810,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T19:45:12.000Z","msg":"好多人俾人煽動左去反00後<br />\n<br />\n其實00後係我地呢代最需要去「拉攏」既一代"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"你 針對 00後 佢哋原本 冇嘢都會變咗 有嘢， 相反你好言相勸 佢哋反而會受"},{"pid":"7a21926603ed9654